</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>New characteristic group</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings as desired. Pay attention to the information given in <a href="#table-create-property-groups">Table 3</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
