<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="520">2.3. Changing characteristics values via group function</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The <strong>group function</strong> allows you to edit the characteristic values for all items linked with this characteristic value at once.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Changing a characteristic’s value with a group function:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
