<h4 id="_deleting_a_property">3.4.1. Deleting a property</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Proceed as described below to irreversibly delete a property if it is no longer needed.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Deleting a property:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>System » System settings » Settings » Properties » Configuration</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong><em>Optional:</em></strong> Select filters to limit the search results.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Start the search.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the property.<br>
→ The detail view of the property opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Delete property</strong>.<br>
→ A window opens and you need to confirm your decision.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Delete</strong>.<br>
→ The property are deleted and removed from the overview.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
