→ The <strong>New barcode</strong> window opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter the name.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the type. Pay attention to the information given in <a href="#table-barcode-types">Table 11</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open the barcode.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Activate one or multiple referrers.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
