<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select the item type <strong>Default</strong>.<br>
<strong>Default</strong> = Creates an item with main variation.<br>
<strong>Multipack</strong> = Creates a <a href="/en/item/combining-products#1000">Multipack</a> item.<br>
