<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Activate to make the variation available if the net stock is positive and unavailable if the net stock is 0 or negative. Both functions complement each other and work in combination with the <strong>To net stock</strong> option under <strong>Limitation</strong>. plentymarkets automatically controls the item’s availability in the online store. Variations do not have to be made invisible if no net stock is available.</p></td>
</tr>
