<strong><em>Note:</em></strong> You can only apply one inheritance setting at a time. As such, all other settings are disabled when you select an inheritance setting.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Execute</strong> to apply the settings to the variations.<br>
<strong><em>Tip:</em></strong> When you change inheritance settings, any main variations you selected in the item overview will be ignored when the group function is run.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
