<p>Go to <strong>Item » Edit item</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open the item.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open the <strong>Variations</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the <strong>filters</strong>. Pay attention to the information given in <a href="#table-filter-variations">Table 45</a>.</p>
</li>
