<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>System » System settings » Orders » Events</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Add event procedure</strong>.<br>
→ The <strong>Create new event procedure</strong> window opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter a name.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the <strong>event</strong> listed in <a href="#table-event-procedure-send-serial-numbers">Table 50</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings. Pay attention to the information given in <a href="#table-event-procedure-send-serial-numbers">Table 50</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Place a check mark next to the option <strong>Active</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
